Yapeng, Niall is correct, I meant that inline comment as a general comment for all the tests.

I realize that the assertTrue looks nicer, but it's definitely weaker.  I'm not familiar enough with these particular tests off the top of my head to say whether the difference really matters for what we're trying to test, so my default position is that we shouldn't make this change.
